298/*



299 * Output and update for atomic system:



300 *    '<S12>/Subsystem1'



301 *    '<S13>/Subsystem2'



302 *    '<S13>/Subsystem3'



303 */



304void NMPC_Controller_Subsystem1(real_T rtu_u, real_T rtu_u_o,



305  B_Subsystem1_NMPC_Controller_T *localB)



306{



307  /* Sqrt: '<S21>/Sqrt' incorporates:



308   *  Math: '<S21>/Math Function2'



309   *  SignalConversion: '<S21>/TmpSignal ConversionAtMath Function2Inport1'



310   *  Sum: '<S21>/Sum of Elements'



311   */



312  localB->Sqrt = sqrt(rtu_u * rtu_u + rtu_u_o * rtu_u_o);



313}



314



315/* Output and update for atomic system: '<S12>/Subsystem4' */



316void NMPC_Controller_Subsystem4(real_T rtu_u, real_T rtu_u_e,



317  B_Subsystem4_NMPC_Controller_T *localB)



318{



319  /* Sum: '<S22>/Sum of Elements' incorporates:



320   *  Math: '<S22>/Math Function2'



321   *  SignalConversion: '<S22>/TmpSignal ConversionAtMath Function2Inport1'



322   */



323  localB->SumofElements = rtu_u * rtu_u + rtu_u_e * rtu_u_e;



324}



325



326/*



327 * Output and update for atomic system:



328 *    '<S13>/Subsystem1'



329 *    '<S14>/Subsystem1'



330 *    '<S30>/Subsystem1'



331 */



332void NMPC_Controller_Subsystem1_j(real_T rtu_u, real_T rtu_u_d, real_T rtu_u_f,



333  B_Subsystem1_NMPC_Controller_l_T *localB)



334{



335  /* Sqrt: '<S23>/Sqrt' incorporates:



336   *  Math: '<S23>/Math Function2'



337   *  SignalConversion: '<S23>/TmpSignal ConversionAtMath Function2Inport1'



338   *  Sum: '<S23>/Sum of Elements'



339   */



340  localB->Sqrt = sqrt((rtu_u * rtu_u + rtu_u_d * rtu_u_d) + rtu_u_f * rtu_u_f);



341}



342



343/* Output and update for atomic system: '<S13>/Subsystem4' */



344void NMPC_Controller_Subsystem4_g(real_T rtu_u, real_T rtu_u_k, real_T rtu_u_j,



345  B_Subsystem4_NMPC_Controller_l_T *localB)



346{



347  /* Sum: '<S26>/Sum of Elements' incorporates:



348   *  Math: '<S26>/Math Function2'



349   *  SignalConversion: '<S26>/TmpSignal ConversionAtMath Function2Inport1'



350   */



351  localB->SumofElements = (rtu_u * rtu_u + rtu_u_k * rtu_u_k) + rtu_u_j *



352    rtu_u_j;



353}



354



355real_T rt_powd_snf(real_T u0, real_T u1)



356{



357  real_T y;



358  real_T tmp;



359  real_T tmp_0;



360  if (rtIsNaN(u0) || rtIsNaN(u1)) {



361    y = (rtNaN);



362  } else {



363    tmp = fabs(u0);



364    tmp_0 = fabs(u1);



365    if (rtIsInf(u1)) {



366      if (tmp == 1.0) {



367        y = (rtNaN);



368      } else if (tmp > 1.0) {



369        if (u1 > 0.0) {



370          y = (rtInf);



371        } else {



372          y = 0.0;



373        }



374      } else if (u1 > 0.0) {



375        y = 0.0;



376      } else {



377        y = (rtInf);



378      }



379    } else if (tmp_0 == 0.0) {



380      y = 1.0;



381    } else if (tmp_0 == 1.0) {



382      if (u1 > 0.0) {



383        y = u0;



384      } else {



385        y = 1.0 / u0;



386      }



387    } else if (u1 == 2.0) {



388      y = u0 * u0;



389    } else if ((u1 == 0.5) && (u0 >= 0.0)) {



390      y = sqrt(u0);



391    } else if ((u0 < 0.0) && (u1 > floor(u1))) {



392      y = (rtNaN);



393    } else {



394      y = pow(u0, u1);



395    }



396  }



397



398  return y;



399}



400



401real_T rt_atan2d_snf(real_T u0, real_T u1)



402{



403  real_T y;



404  int32_T u0_0;



405  int32_T u1_0;



406  if (rtIsNaN(u0) || rtIsNaN(u1)) {



407    y = (rtNaN);



408  } else if (rtIsInf(u0) && rtIsInf(u1)) {



409    if (u0 > 0.0) {



410      u0_0 = 1;



411    } else {



412      u0_0 = -1;



413    }



414



415    if (u1 > 0.0) {



416      u1_0 = 1;



417    } else {



418      u1_0 = -1;



419    }



420



421    y = atan2(u0_0, u1_0);



422  } else if (u1 == 0.0) {



423    if (u0 > 0.0) {



424      y = RT_PI / 2.0;



425    } else if (u0 < 0.0) {



426      y = -(RT_PI / 2.0);



427    } else {



428      y = 0.0;



429    }



430  } else {



431    y = atan2(u0, u1);



432  }



433



434  return y;



435}

437/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/Control System' */



438static void NMPC_Controller_ann_norm_X(const real_T x_ann_un[7], const real_T



439  minXin[7], const real_T maxXin[7], real_T minYin, real_T maxYin, real_T x_ann



440  [7])



441{



442  int32_T i;



443



444  /* %%x_ann_un dimension is [number of inputs,ann_samples] */



445  /* %number of samples */



446  /* %allocation */



447  for (i = 0; i < 7; i++) {



448    x_ann[i] = (x_ann_un[i] - minXin[i]) * (maxYin - minYin) / (maxXin[i] -



449      minXin[i]) + minYin;



450  }



451}



452



453/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/Control System' */



454static real_T NMPC_Controller_ann_denorm_Y(real_T y_ann, real_T minXout, real_T



455  maxXout, real_T minYout, real_T maxYout)



456{



457  /* %%y_ann_un dimension is [ann_samples,number of inputs] */



458  /* %number of samples */



459  /* %allocation */



460  return (y_ann - minYout) * (maxXout - minXout) / (maxYout - minYout) + minXout;



461}

463/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/Control System' */



464static real_T NMPC_Controller_norm(const real_T x[2])



465{



466  real_T y;



467  real_T scale;



468  real_T absxk;



469  real_T t;



470  scale = 2.2250738585072014E-308;



471  absxk = fabs(x[0]);



472  if (absxk > 2.2250738585072014E-308) {



473    y = 1.0;



474    scale = absxk;



475  } else {



476    t = absxk / 2.2250738585072014E-308;



477    y = t * t;



478  }



479



480  absxk = fabs(x[1]);



481  if (absxk > scale) {



482    t = scale / absxk;



483    y = y * t * t + 1.0;



484    scale = absxk;



485  } else {



486    t = absxk / scale;



487    y += t * t;



488  }



489



490  return scale * sqrt(y);



491}



492



493/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/Control System' */



494static real_T NMPC_Controller_norm_l(const real_T x[3])



495{



496  real_T y;



497  real_T scale;



498  real_T absxk;



499  real_T t;



500  scale = 2.2250738585072014E-308;



501  absxk = fabs(x[0]);



502  if (absxk > 2.2250738585072014E-308) {



503    y = 1.0;



504    scale = absxk;



505  } else {



506    t = absxk / 2.2250738585072014E-308;



507    y = t * t;



508  }



509



510  absxk = fabs(x[1]);



511  if (absxk > scale) {



512    t = scale / absxk;



513    y = y * t * t + 1.0;



514    scale = absxk;



515  } else {



516    t = absxk / scale;



517    y += t * t;



518  }



519



520  absxk = fabs(x[2]);



521  if (absxk > scale) {



522    t = scale / absxk;



523    y = y * t * t + 1.0;



524    scale = absxk;



525  } else {



526    t = absxk / scale;



527    y += t * t;



528  }



529



530  return scale * sqrt(y);



531}

584  *accelZ_ann_k, real_T z_augm_k[12], real_T e_augm_k[4], real_T *THL_kk, real_T



585  *EL_kk, real_T *AIL_kk, real_T *RDR_kk, real_T *VT_kk, real_T *alpha_kk,



586  real_T *beta_kk, real_T *phi_kk, real_T *theta_kk, real_T *psi_kk, real_T



587  *P_kk, real_T *Q_kk, real_T *R_kk, real_T *falpha_k, real_T *fbeta_k, real_T



588  *n_kk, real_T *e_kk, real_T *h_kk, real_T *ro_kk, real_T *xw11_kk, real_T



589  *xw12_kk, real_T *xw13_kk, real_T *xw14_kk, real_T *xw21_kk, real_T *xw22_kk,



590  real_T *xw23_kk, real_T *xw24_kk, real_T *xw31_kk, real_T *xw32_kk, real_T



591  *xw33_kk, real_T *xw34_kk)



592{



593  real_T mass;



594  real_T delta_I;



595  real_T c2;



596  real_T c4;



597  real_T Qbar_k;



598  real_T U_k;



599  real_T V_k;



600  real_T W_k;



601  real_T CL_k;



602  real_T CD_k;



603  real_T Cls_k;



604  real_T Cms_k;



605  real_T Cns_k;



606  real_T Cl_k;



607  real_T Cn_k;



608  real_T Udot_k;



609  real_T Vdot_k;



610  real_T Wdot_k;



611  real_T fn_k;



612  real_T fe_k;



613  real_T fh_k;



614  uint8_T next_wpt_index;



615  real_T ea;



616  real_T hd_k;



617  real_T nd_k;



618  real_T ed_k;



619  real_T atrack;



620  int32_T factor;



621  real_T btrack;



622  real_T edot_track_k;



623  real_T ndot_track_k;



624  real_T r_a;



625  real_T s_a;



626  real_T t_a;



627  real_T er_k_0[2];



628  real_T er_k_1[3];



629  real_T nr_k_0[2];



630  real_T fn_k_0[2];



631  real_T VT_k_0[7];



632  real_T VT_k_1[7];



633  real_T VT_k_2[7];



634  real_T tmp[7];



635  real_T w_ann_X_0[40];



636  int32_T i;



637



638  /* %temporary */



639  /* %%%uas at time [k]%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



640  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



641  /* %mass and inertia coefficients%% */



642  mass = b_weight / b_g;



643  delta_I = b_IxxB * b_IzzB - b_IxzB * b_IxzB;



644  c2 = ((b_IxxB - b_IyyB) + b_IzzB) * b_IxzB / delta_I;



645  c4 = b_IxzB / delta_I;



646



647  /* %dynamic pressure%% */



648  Qbar_k = 0.5 * b_rho * (VT_k * VT_k);



649



650  /* %body velocities%% */



651  U_k = VT_k * cos(alpha_k) * cos(beta_k);



652  V_k = VT_k * sin(beta_k);



653  W_k = VT_k * sin(alpha_k) * cos(beta_k);



654



655  /* %aerodynamic coefficients%% */



656  CL_k = ((((Q_k - b_Qtrim) * b_CLq * b_Cbar / 2.0 / b_Utrim + (b_CLa * alpha_k



657             + b_CL0)) + b_CLadot * alphadot_k * b_Cbar / 2.0 / b_Utrim) + (U_k



658           - b_Utrim) * b_CLu / b_Utrim) + b_CLde * EL_k;



659



660  /* CD_k=CD0+CDa*alpha_k+CDq*(Q_k-Qtrim)*Cbar/2/Utrim+CDadot*alphadot_k*Cbar/2/Utrim+CDu*(U_k-Utrim)/Utrim+CDde*EL_k; %lin */



661  CD_k = ((((CL_k * CL_k / (3.1415926535897931 * b_b / b_Cbar * 0.87) +



662             b_CD0_bar) + (Q_k - b_Qtrim) * b_CDq * b_Cbar / 2.0 / b_Utrim) +



663           b_CDadot * alphadot_k * b_Cbar / 2.0 / b_Utrim) + (U_k - b_Utrim) *



664          b_CDu / b_Utrim) + b_CDde * EL_k;



665



666  /* nonlin */



667  Cls_k = ((((P_k - b_Ptrim) * b_Clp * b_b / 2.0 / b_Utrim + b_Clb * beta_k) +



668            (R_k - b_Rtrim) * b_Clr * b_b / 2.0 / b_Utrim) + b_Clda * AIL_k) +



669    b_Cldr * RDR_k;



670  Cms_k = ((((Q_k - b_Qtrim) * b_Cmq * b_Cbar / 2.0 / b_Utrim + (b_Cma * alpha_k



671              + b_Cm0)) + b_Cmadot * alphadot_k * b_Cbar / 2.0 / b_Utrim) + (U_k



672            - b_Utrim) * b_Cmu / b_Utrim) + b_Cmde * EL_k;



673  Cns_k = ((((P_k - b_Ptrim) * b_Cnp * b_b / 2.0 / b_Utrim + b_Cnb * beta_k) +



674            (R_k - b_Rtrim) * b_Cnr * b_b / 2.0 / b_Utrim) + b_Cnda * AIL_k) +



675    b_Cndr * RDR_k;



676  Cl_k = Cls_k * cos(alpha_k) - Cns_k * sin(alpha_k);



677  Cn_k = Cls_k * sin(alpha_k) + Cns_k * cos(alpha_k);



678



679  /* %engine thrust%% */



680  Cls_k = 100.0 * THL_k;



681



682  /* %S&C aerodynamic and thrust linear accelerations%% */



683  *accelX_scd_k = (((Cls_k * Cls_k * b_xT2 + 100.0 * THL_k * b_xT1) + b_xT0) + (



684    -CD_k * cos(alpha_k) + CL_k * sin(alpha_k)) * (Qbar_k * b_S)) / mass;



685



686  /* [ft/s2] */



687  *accelY_scd_k = (((((P_k - b_Ptrim) * b_Cyp * b_b / 2.0 / b_Utrim + b_Cyb *



688                      beta_k) + (R_k - b_Rtrim) * b_Cyr * b_b / 2.0 / b_Utrim) +



689                    b_Cyda * AIL_k) + b_Cydr * RDR_k) * (Qbar_k * b_S) / mass;



690



691  /* [ft/s2] */



692  *accelZ_scd_k = (-CD_k * sin(alpha_k) - CL_k * cos(alpha_k)) * (Qbar_k * b_S) /



693    mass;



694



695  /* [ft/s2] */



696  /* ANN linear accelerations */



697  /* X-axis */



698  VT_k_2[0] = VT_k;



699  VT_k_2[1] = alpha_k;



700  VT_k_2[2] = beta_k;



701  VT_k_2[3] = Q_k;



702  VT_k_2[4] = alphadot_k;



703  VT_k_2[5] = THL_k;



704  VT_k_2[6] = EL_k;



705  NMPC_Controller_ann_norm_X(VT_k_2, b_X_minXin, b_X_maxXin, b_X_minYin,



706    b_X_maxYin, tmp);



707  for (factor = 0; factor < 40; factor++) {



708    r_a = 0.0;



709    for (i = 0; i < 7; i++) {



710      r_a += w_ann_X[40 * i + factor] * tmp[i];



711    }



712



713    w_ann_X_0[factor] = r_a + b_ann_X[factor];



714  }



715



716  r_a = 0.0;



717  for (factor = 0; factor < 40; factor++) {



718    r_a += a_ann_X[factor] * w_ann_X_0[factor];



719  }



720



721  *accelX_ann_k = NMPC_Controller_ann_denorm_Y(r_a + c_ann_X, b_X_minXout,



722    b_X_maxXout, b_X_minYout, b_X_maxYout) * b_g;



723



724  /* [ft/s2] no tansig */



725  /* Y_axis */



726  VT_k_1[0] = VT_k;



727  VT_k_1[1] = beta_k;



728  VT_k_1[2] = P_k;



729  VT_k_1[3] = R_k;



730  VT_k_1[4] = betadot_k;



731  VT_k_1[5] = AIL_k;



732  VT_k_1[6] = RDR_k;



733  NMPC_Controller_ann_norm_X(VT_k_1, b_Y_minXin, b_Y_maxXin, b_Y_minYin,



734    b_Y_maxYin, tmp);



735  for (factor = 0; factor < 40; factor++) {



736    r_a = 0.0;



737    for (i = 0; i < 7; i++) {



738      r_a += w_ann_Y[40 * i + factor] * tmp[i];



739    }



740



741    w_ann_X_0[factor] = r_a + b_ann_Y[factor];



742  }



743



744  r_a = 0.0;



745  for (factor = 0; factor < 40; factor++) {



746    r_a += a_ann_Y[factor] * w_ann_X_0[factor];



747  }



748



749  *accelY_ann_k = NMPC_Controller_ann_denorm_Y(r_a + c_ann_Y, b_Y_minXout,



750    b_Y_maxXout, b_Y_minYout, b_Y_maxYout) * b_g;



751



752  /* [ft/s2] no tansig */



753  /* Z-axis */



754  VT_k_0[0] = VT_k;



755  VT_k_0[1] = alpha_k;



756  VT_k_0[2] = beta_k;



757  VT_k_0[3] = Q_k;



758  VT_k_0[4] = alphadot_k;



759  VT_k_0[5] = THL_k;



760  VT_k_0[6] = EL_k;



761  NMPC_Controller_ann_norm_X(VT_k_0, b_Z_minXin, b_Z_maxXin, b_Z_minYin,



762    b_Z_maxYin, tmp);



763  for (factor = 0; factor < 40; factor++) {



764    r_a = 0.0;



765    for (i = 0; i < 7; i++) {



766      r_a += w_ann_Z[40 * i + factor] * tmp[i];



767    }



768



769    w_ann_X_0[factor] = r_a + b_ann_Z[factor];



770  }



771



772  r_a = 0.0;



773  for (factor = 0; factor < 40; factor++) {



774    r_a += a_ann_Z[factor] * w_ann_X_0[factor];



775  }



776



777  *accelZ_ann_k = NMPC_Controller_ann_denorm_Y(r_a + c_ann_Z, b_Z_minXout,



778    b_Z_maxXout, b_Z_minYout, b_Z_maxYout) * b_g;



779



780  /* [ft/s2] no tansig */



781  Cls_k = 0.0;



782



783  /* initialization */



784  Cns_k = 0.0;



785



786  /* initialization */



787  mass = 0.0;



788



789  /* initialization */



790  if (FL_ann == 0.0) {



791    /* scd */



792    Cls_k = *accelX_scd_k;



793    Cns_k = *accelY_scd_k;



794    mass = *accelZ_scd_k;



795  } else {



796    if (FL_ann == 1.0) {



797      /* ann */



798      Cls_k = *accelX_ann_k;



799      Cns_k = *accelY_ann_k;



800      mass = *accelZ_ann_k;



801    }



802  }



803



804  /* body accelerations */



805  Udot_k = ((R_k * V_k - Q_k * W_k) - b_g * sin(theta_k)) + Cls_k;



806  Vdot_k = ((P_k * W_k - R_k * U_k) + b_g * sin(phi_k) * cos(theta_k)) + Cns_k;



807  Wdot_k = ((Q_k * U_k - P_k * V_k) + b_g * cos(phi_k) * cos(theta_k)) + mass;



808



809  /* %inertial speed (with no wind)%% */



810  fn_k = ((sin(phi_k) * sin(theta_k) * cos(psi_k) - cos(phi_k) * sin(psi_k)) *



811          V_k + U_k * cos(theta_k) * cos(psi_k)) + (cos(phi_k) * sin(theta_k) *



812    cos(psi_k) + sin(phi_k) * sin(psi_k)) * W_k;



813  fe_k = ((sin(phi_k) * sin(theta_k) * sin(psi_k) + cos(phi_k) * cos(psi_k)) *



814          V_k + U_k * cos(theta_k) * sin(psi_k)) + (cos(phi_k) * sin(theta_k) *



815    sin(psi_k) - sin(phi_k) * cos(psi_k)) * W_k;



816  fh_k = (U_k * sin(theta_k) - V_k * sin(phi_k) * cos(theta_k)) - W_k * cos



817    (phi_k) * cos(theta_k);



818



819  /* %inertial speed%% */



820  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



821  /* %%%uas at time [k]%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



822  /* %%%trajectory logic at time [k]%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



823  /* Local variable assignment */



824  *wpt_index_kk = wpt_index_k;



825  *home_reset_kk = home_reset_k;



826



827  /* PIC/CIC Transition Logic: */



828  /*  On transition to CIC or PIC, set index = 0 and current position to  */



829  /*  current waypoint; hold current waypoint. */



830  if ((sw > (real_T)pic_cic_k) || (sw == 0.0)) {



831    start_wpt_k[0] = h_k;



832    start_wpt_k[1] = n_k;



833    start_wpt_k[2] = e_k;



834    *wpt_index_kk = 0U;



835    *home_reset_kk = 0U;



836  }



837



838  /*  Change the waypoint index when home command */



839  if ((home_cmd == 1) && (sw == 1.0) && (*home_reset_kk == 0)) {



840    *wpt_index_kk = 23U;



841    *home_reset_kk = 1U;



842  }



843



844  /* OP trajectory generation */



845  /* %reassigning the a and b waypoints */



846  if ((b_TR == 2.0) && (*home_reset_kk == 0)) {



847    *wpt_index_kk = 1U;



848    wpts_n[wpt_index_k - 1] = n_op_k - 100.0 * vn_op_k;



849    factor = (int32_T)(wpt_index_k + 1U);



850    if ((uint32_T)factor > 255U) {



851      factor = 255;



852    }



853



854    wpts_n[factor - 1] = 100.0 * vn_op_k + n_op_k;



855    wpts_e[wpt_index_k - 1] = e_op_k - 100.0 * ve_op_k;



856    factor = (int32_T)(wpt_index_k + 1U);



857    if ((uint32_T)factor > 255U) {



858      factor = 255;



859    }



860



861    wpts_e[factor - 1] = 100.0 * ve_op_k + e_op_k;



862    wpts_h[wpt_index_k - 1] = h_op_k - 100.0 * vh_op_k;



863    factor = (int32_T)(wpt_index_k + 1U);



864    if ((uint32_T)factor > 255U) {



865      factor = 255;



866    }



867



868    wpts_h[factor - 1] = 100.0 * vh_op_k + h_op_k;



869  }



870



871  /* calculate the next waypoint index */



872  factor = (int32_T)(*wpt_index_kk + 1U);



873  if ((uint32_T)factor > 255U) {



874    factor = 255;



875  }



876



877  next_wpt_index = (uint8_T)factor;



878



879  /* beyond final point (fp), go to return point (rp) */



880  if ((uint8_T)factor > wpts_fp) {



881    next_wpt_index = wpts_rp;



882  }



883



884  /* calculate distance to next waypoint */



885  Cls_k = n_k - wpts_n[next_wpt_index - 1];



886  Cns_k = e_k - wpts_e[next_wpt_index - 1];



887  Cls_k = sqrt(Cls_k * Cls_k + Cns_k * Cns_k);



888



889  /* change to next waypoint if in range */



890  if ((Cls_k < b_dist2b) && (sw == 1.0)) {



891    /*  Do not change index if sw=0 */



892    *wpt_index_kk = next_wpt_index;



893    if (next_wpt_index == wpts_fp) {



894      next_wpt_index = wpts_rp;



895    } else {



896      factor = (int32_T)(next_wpt_index + 1U);



897      if ((uint32_T)factor > 255U) {



898        factor = 255;



899      }



900



901      next_wpt_index = (uint8_T)factor;



902    }



903  }



904



905  /* function outputs */



906  if ((*wpt_index_kk == 0) || (*wpt_index_kk == 23)) {



907    /*  Assign the speed of the starting segment to the speed of the first */



908    /*  waypoint */



909    *Vab_k = wpts_v[0];



910    CL_k = start_wpt_k[0];



911    CD_k = start_wpt_k[1];



912    ea = start_wpt_k[2];



913  } else {



914    *Vab_k = wpts_v[*wpt_index_kk - 1];



915    CL_k = wpts_h[*wpt_index_kk - 1];



916    CD_k = wpts_n[*wpt_index_kk - 1];



917    ea = wpts_e[*wpt_index_kk - 1];



918  }



919



920  *distance2b = (real32_T)Cls_k;



921  *pic_cic_kk = sw;



922



923  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



924  /* %%%trajectory logic at time [k]%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



925  /* %%%guidance system at time [k]%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



926  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



927  /* %reference point r%% */



928  Cls_k = wpts_h[next_wpt_index - 1] - CL_k;



929  Cns_k = wpts_n[next_wpt_index - 1] - CD_k;



930  mass = wpts_e[next_wpt_index - 1] - ea;



931  Cls_k = (((wpts_h[next_wpt_index - 1] - CL_k) * (h_k - CL_k) +



932            (wpts_n[next_wpt_index - 1] - CD_k) * (n_k - CD_k)) +



933           (wpts_e[next_wpt_index - 1] - ea) * (e_k - ea)) / ((Cls_k * Cls_k +



934    Cns_k * Cns_k) + mass * mass);



935  hd_k = (wpts_h[next_wpt_index - 1] - CL_k) * Cls_k + CL_k;



936  nd_k = (wpts_n[next_wpt_index - 1] - CD_k) * Cls_k + CD_k;



937  ed_k = (wpts_e[next_wpt_index - 1] - ea) * Cls_k + ea;



938  Cls_k = wpts_h[next_wpt_index - 1] - hd_k;



939  Cns_k = wpts_n[next_wpt_index - 1] - nd_k;



940  mass = wpts_e[next_wpt_index - 1] - ed_k;



941  Cls_k = b_L / sqrt((Cls_k * Cls_k + Cns_k * Cns_k) + mass * mass);



942  *er_k = (wpts_e[next_wpt_index - 1] - ed_k) * Cls_k + ed_k;



943  *nr_k = (wpts_n[next_wpt_index - 1] - nd_k) * Cls_k + nd_k;



944  *hr_k = (wpts_h[next_wpt_index - 1] - hd_k) * Cls_k + hd_k;



945



946  /* %alpha and beta track%% */



947  Cls_k = wpts_h[next_wpt_index - 1] - CL_k;



948  Cns_k = wpts_n[next_wpt_index - 1] - CD_k;



949  mass = wpts_e[next_wpt_index - 1] - ea;



950  atrack = asin((wpts_h[next_wpt_index - 1] - CL_k) / sqrt((Cls_k * Cls_k +



951    Cns_k * Cns_k) + mass * mass));



952  Cls_k = wpts_n[next_wpt_index - 1] - CD_k;



953  Cns_k = wpts_e[next_wpt_index - 1] - ea;



954  factor = 1;



955  mass = 0.0;



956  if (!((wpts_n[next_wpt_index - 1] - CD_k > 0.0) && (wpts_e[next_wpt_index - 1]



957        - ea > 0.0))) {



958    if ((wpts_n[next_wpt_index - 1] - CD_k > 0.0) && (wpts_e[next_wpt_index - 1]



959         - ea < 0.0)) {



960      mass = 3.1415926535897931;



961      factor = -1;



962    } else {



963      if ((wpts_n[next_wpt_index - 1] - CD_k < 0.0) && (wpts_e[next_wpt_index -



964           1] - ea < 0.0)) {



965        mass = -3.1415926535897931;



966        factor = -1;



967      }



968    }



969  }



970



971  btrack = asin((wpts_n[next_wpt_index - 1] - CD_k) / sqrt(Cls_k * Cls_k + Cns_k



972    * Cns_k)) * (real_T)factor + mass;



973



974  /* %edot, ndot and hdot relative to track%% */



975  edot_track_k = (sin(atrack) * cos(btrack) * fh_k + sin(btrack) * fn_k) + cos



976    (atrack) * cos(btrack) * fe_k;



977  ndot_track_k = (-sin(atrack) * sin(btrack) * fh_k + cos(btrack) * fn_k) - cos



978    (atrack) * sin(btrack) * fe_k;



979



980  /* %er-e, nr-n and hr-h relative to track%% */



981  /* %etaLon at time [k]%% */



982  nr_k_0[0] = *nr_k - n_k;



983  nr_k_0[1] = *er_k - e_k;



984  fn_k_0[0] = fn_k;



985  fn_k_0[1] = fe_k;



986  *etaLon_k = rt_atan2d_snf(*hr_k - h_k, NMPC_Controller_norm(nr_k_0)) -



987    rt_atan2d_snf(fh_k, NMPC_Controller_norm(fn_k_0));



988



989  /* %etaLat at time [k]%% */



990  Cls_k = rt_atan2d_snf(ndot_track_k, edot_track_k) - rt_atan2d_snf((-sin(atrack)



991    * sin(btrack) * (*hr_k - h_k) + (*nr_k - n_k) * cos(btrack)) - cos(atrack) *



992    sin(btrack) * (*er_k - e_k), (sin(atrack) * cos(btrack) * (*hr_k - h_k) +



993    (*nr_k - n_k) * sin(btrack)) + cos(atrack) * cos(btrack) * (*er_k - e_k));



994  *etaLat_k = Cls_k;



995  if (Cls_k > 3.1415926535897931) {



996    *etaLat_k = Cls_k - 6.2831853071795862;



997  }



998



999  if (Cls_k < -3.1415926535897931) {



1000    *etaLat_k = Cls_k + 6.2831853071795862;



1001  }



1002



1003  /* OP trajectory generation */



1004  /* reassigning Vab (based on the new d point) */



1005  if (b_TR == 2.0) {



1006    CL_k = wpts_n[next_wpt_index - 1] - n_op_k;



1007    CD_k = wpts_e[next_wpt_index - 1] - e_op_k;



1008    ea = wpts_h[next_wpt_index - 1] - h_op_k;



1009    r_a = wpts_n[next_wpt_index - 1] - nd_k;



1010    s_a = wpts_e[next_wpt_index - 1] - ed_k;



1011    t_a = wpts_h[next_wpt_index - 1] - hd_k;



1012    mass = nd_k - n_op_k;



1013    Cns_k = ed_k - e_op_k;



1014    Cls_k = hd_k - h_op_k;



1015    r_a = sqrt((CL_k * CL_k + CD_k * CD_k) + ea * ea) - sqrt((r_a * r_a + s_a *



1016      s_a) + t_a * t_a);



1017    if (r_a < 0.0) {



1018      r_a = -1.0;



1019    } else if (r_a > 0.0) {



1020      r_a = 1.0;



1021    } else {



1022      if (r_a == 0.0) {



1023        r_a = 0.0;



1024      }



1025    }



1026



1027    *Vab_k = sqrt((vn_op_k * vn_op_k + ve_op_k * ve_op_k) + vh_op_k * vh_op_k) -



1028      atan(sqrt((mass * mass + Cns_k * Cns_k) + Cls_k * Cls_k) * r_a / 100.0) *



1029      0.063661977236758135;



1030



1031    /* (168.78) (5) (/100) */



1032  }



1033



1034  /* %VT theta phi and beta command%% */



1035  /* %consider wind in VTcmd [0]: no [1]:yes */



1036  mass = *Vab_k * cos(atrack) * sin(btrack) + 0.0 * sw;



1037  Cns_k = *Vab_k * cos(atrack) * cos(btrack) + 0.0 * sw;



1038  Cls_k = *Vab_k * sin(atrack) + 0.0 * sw;



1039  *VTcmd_k = sqrt((mass * mass + Cns_k * Cns_k) + Cls_k * Cls_k);



1040  Cls_k = atan(*etaLon_k * sw);



1041  er_k_1[0] = *er_k - e_k;



1042  er_k_1[1] = *nr_k - n_k;



1043  er_k_1[2] = *hr_k - h_k;



1044  *thetacmd_k = rt_atan2d_snf(((fe_k * fe_k + fn_k * fn_k) + fh_k * fh_k) * 2.0 *



1045                              (Cls_k * b_KpLon + ro_k), NMPC_Controller_norm_l



1046    (er_k_1));



1047  er_k_0[0] = *er_k - e_k;



1048  er_k_0[1] = *nr_k - n_k;



1049  *phicmd_k = rt_atan2d_snf((edot_track_k * edot_track_k + ndot_track_k *



1050    ndot_track_k) * 2.0 * b_KpLat * sw * *etaLat_k, NMPC_Controller_norm(er_k_0));



1051



1052  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



1053  /* %%%guidance system at time [k]%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



1054  /* %%%implementing saturation of actuators%% */



1055  /* %deflection max and min */



1056  if (THL_k > b_ThrottleMax) {



1057    THL_k = b_ThrottleMax;



1058  } else {



1059    if (THL_k < b_ThrottleMin) {



1060      THL_k = b_ThrottleMin;



1061    }



1062  }



1063



1064  if (EL_k > b_ElevatorMax) {



1065    EL_k = b_ElevatorMax;



1066  } else {



1067    if (EL_k < b_ElevatorMin) {



1068      EL_k = b_ElevatorMin;



1069    }



1070  }



1071



1072  if (AIL_k > b_AileronMax) {



1073    AIL_k = b_AileronMax;



1074  } else {



1075    if (AIL_k < b_AileronMin) {



1076      AIL_k = b_AileronMin;



1077    }



1078  }



1079



1080  if (RDR_k > b_RudderMax) {



1081    RDR_k = b_RudderMax;



1082  } else {



1083    if (RDR_k < b_RudderMin) {



1084      RDR_k = b_RudderMin;



1085    }



1086  }



1087



1088  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



1089  /* %%%prediction of kk%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



1090  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



1091  /* %longitudinal guidance integrator */



1092  *ro_kk = b_dt * Cls_k * b_KiLon + ro_k;



1093



1094  /* %servos prediction%% */



1095  *THL_kk = (b_Athrottle * THL_k + b_Bthrottle * THLcmd_k) * b_dt + THL_k;



1096  *EL_kk = (b_Aelevator * EL_k + b_Belevator * ELcmd_k) * b_dt + EL_k;



1097  *AIL_kk = (b_Aaileron * AIL_k + b_Baileron * AILcmd_k) * b_dt + AIL_k;



1098  *RDR_kk = (b_Arudder * RDR_k + b_Brudder * RDRcmd_k) * b_dt + RDR_k;



1099



1100  /* %UAV prediction%% */



1101  Cls_k = ((U_k * Udot_k + V_k * Vdot_k) + W_k * Wdot_k) / VT_k;



1102  *falpha_k = (U_k * Wdot_k - W_k * Udot_k) / (U_k * U_k + W_k * W_k);



1103  *fbeta_k = (VT_k * Vdot_k - V_k * Cls_k) / (U_k * U_k + W_k * W_k) * cos



1104    (beta_k);



1105  *VT_kk = b_dt * Cls_k + VT_k;



1106  *alpha_kk = b_dt * *falpha_k + alpha_k;



1107  *beta_kk = b_dt * *fbeta_k + beta_k;



1108  *phi_kk = ((R_k * cos(phi_k) + Q_k * sin(phi_k)) * tan(theta_k) + P_k) * b_dt



1109    + phi_k;



1110  *theta_kk = (Q_k * cos(phi_k) - R_k * sin(phi_k)) * b_dt + theta_k;



1111  *psi_kk = (R_k * cos(phi_k) + Q_k * sin(phi_k)) / cos(theta_k) * b_dt + psi_k;



1112  *P_kk = ((((b_IyyB - b_IzzB) * b_IzzB - b_IxzB * b_IxzB) / delta_I * R_k + c2 *



1113            P_k) * Q_k + (b_IzzB / delta_I * Cl_k + c4 * Cn_k) * (Qbar_k * b_S *



1114            b_b)) * b_dt + P_k;



1115  *Q_kk = (((b_IzzB - b_IxxB) / b_IyyB * P_k * R_k - (P_k * P_k - R_k * R_k) *



1116            (b_IxzB / b_IyyB)) + Qbar_k * b_S * b_Cbar * (1.0 / b_IyyB) * Cms_k)



1117    * b_dt + Q_k;



1118  *R_kk = ((((b_IxxB - b_IyyB) * b_IxxB + b_IxzB * b_IxzB) / delta_I * P_k - c2 *



1119            R_k) * Q_k + (b_IxxB / delta_I * Cn_k + c4 * Cl_k) * (Qbar_k * b_S *



1120            b_b)) * b_dt + R_k;



1121



1122  /* %inertial frame prediction%% */



1123  *n_kk = b_dt * fn_k + n_k;



1124  *e_kk = b_dt * fe_k + e_k;



1125  *h_kk = b_dt * fh_k + h_k;



1126



1127  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



1128  /* %%%prediction of kk%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



1129  /* %%%Robustness nmpc calculations%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



1130  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



1131  /* %outputs e, y and z%% */



1132  e_augm_k[0] = *VTcmd_k - VT_k;



1133  e_augm_k[1] = *thetacmd_k - theta_k;



1134  e_augm_k[2] = *phicmd_k - phi_k;



1135  e_augm_k[3] = 0.0 - beta_k;



1136



1137  /* %Robustness states at [k+1]%% */



1138  *xw11_kk = b_W11d.a * xw11_k + b_W11d.b * e_augm_k[0];



1139



1140  /* W11 e_VT */



1141  *xw12_kk = b_W12d.a * xw12_k + b_W12d.b * e_augm_k[1];



1142



1143  /* W12 e_theta */



1144  *xw13_kk = b_W13d.a * xw13_k + b_W13d.b * e_augm_k[2];



1145



1146  /* W13 e_phi */



1147  *xw14_kk = (0.0 - beta_k) * b_W14d.b + b_W14d.a * xw14_k;



1148



1149  /* W14 e_beta */



1150  *xw21_kk = b_W21d.a * xw21_k + b_W21d.b * THLcmd_k;



1151



1152  /* W21 Throttle cmd */



1153  *xw22_kk = b_W22d.a * xw22_k + b_W22d.b * ELcmd_k;



1154



1155  /* W22 Elevator cmd */



1156  *xw23_kk = b_W23d.a * xw23_k + b_W23d.b * AILcmd_k;



1157



1158  /* W23 Aileron cmd */



1159  *xw24_kk = b_W24d.a * xw24_k + b_W24d.b * RDRcmd_k;



1160



1161  /* W24 Rudder cmd */



1162  *xw31_kk = b_W31d.a * xw31_k + b_W31d.b * VT_k;



1163



1164  /* W31 VT */



1165  *xw32_kk = b_W32d.a * xw32_k + b_W32d.b * theta_k;



1166



1167  /* W32 theta */



1168  *xw33_kk = b_W33d.a * xw33_k + b_W33d.b * phi_k;



1169



1170  /* W33 phi */



1171  *xw34_kk = b_W34d.a * xw34_k + b_W34d.b * beta_k;



1172



1173  /* W34 beta */



1174  /* %Robustness output at [k] */



1175  z_augm_k[0] = b_W11d.c * xw11_k + b_W11d.d * e_augm_k[0];



1176



1177  /* W11 e_VT */



1178  z_augm_k[1] = b_W12d.c * xw12_k + b_W12d.d * e_augm_k[1];



1179



1180  /* W12 e_theta */



1181  z_augm_k[2] = b_W13d.c * xw13_k + b_W13d.d * e_augm_k[2];



1182



1183  /* W13 e_phi */



1184  z_augm_k[3] = (0.0 - beta_k) * b_W14d.d + b_W14d.c * xw14_k;



1185



1186  /* W14 e_beta */



1187  z_augm_k[4] = b_W21d.c * xw21_k + b_W21d.d * THLcmd_k;



1188



1189  /* W21 Throttle cmd */



1190  z_augm_k[5] = b_W22d.c * xw22_k + b_W22d.d * ELcmd_k;



1191



1192  /* W22 Elevator cmd */



1193  z_augm_k[6] = b_W23d.c * xw23_k + b_W23d.d * AILcmd_k;



1194



1195  /* W23 Aileron cmd */



1196  z_augm_k[7] = b_W24d.c * xw24_k + b_W24d.d * RDRcmd_k;



1197



1198  /* W24 Rudder cmd */



1199  z_augm_k[8] = b_W31d.c * xw31_k + b_W31d.d * VT_k;



1200



1201  /* W31 VT */



1202  z_augm_k[9] = b_W32d.c * xw32_k + b_W32d.d * theta_k;



1203



1204  /* W32 theta */



1205  z_augm_k[10] = b_W33d.c * xw33_k + b_W33d.d * phi_k;



1206



1207  /* W33 phi */



1208  z_augm_k[11] = b_W34d.c * xw34_k + b_W34d.d * beta_k;



1209



1210  /* W34 beta */



1211  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



1212  /* %%%Robustness nmpc calculations%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



1213}

1215/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/Control System' */



1216static void NMPC_Controller_eml_ipiv2perm(const int32_T ipiv[80], int32_T perm



1217  [80])



1218{



1219  int32_T pipk;



1220  int32_T k;



1221  for (k = 0; k < 80; k++) {



1222    perm[k] = 1 + k;



1223  }



1224



1225  for (k = 0; k < 79; k++) {



1226    if (ipiv[k] > 1 + k) {



1227      pipk = perm[ipiv[k] - 1];



1228      perm[ipiv[k] - 1] = perm[k];



1229      perm[k] = pipk;



1230    }



1231  }



1232}

1234/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/Control System' */



1235static void NMPC_Controller_eml_xtrsm(const real_T A[6400], real_T B[6400])



1236{



1237  int32_T jBcol;



1238  int32_T kAcol;



1239  int32_T j;



1240  int32_T k;



1241  int32_T i;



1242  for (j = 0; j < 80; j++) {



1243    jBcol = 80 * j;



1244    for (k = 79; k >= 0; k += -1) {



1245      kAcol = 80 * k;



1246      if (B[k + jBcol] != 0.0) {



1247        B[k + jBcol] /= A[k + kAcol];



1248        for (i = 0; i + 1 <= k; i++) {



1249          B[i + jBcol] -= B[k + jBcol] * A[i + kAcol];



1250        }



1251      }



1252    }



1253  }



1254}

1256/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/Control System' */



1257static void NMPC_Controller_eml_xswap(real_T x[6400], int32_T ix0, int32_T iy0)



1258{



1259  int32_T ix;



1260  int32_T iy;



1261  real_T temp;



1262  int32_T k;



1263  ix = ix0 - 1;



1264  iy = iy0 - 1;



1265  for (k = 0; k < 80; k++) {



1266    temp = x[ix];



1267    x[ix] = x[iy];



1268    x[iy] = temp;



1269    ix += 80;



1270    iy += 80;



1271  }



1272}

1274/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/Control System' */



1275static void NMPC_Controller_invNxN(const real_T x[6400], real_T y[6400])



1276{



1277  int32_T p[80];



1278  int32_T c;



1279  int32_T j;



1280  int32_T ipiv[80];



1281  int32_T b_j;



1282  int32_T c_c;



1283  real_T smax;



1284  real_T s;



1285  int32_T jA;



1286  int32_T b_ix;



1287  int32_T e;



1288  int32_T ijA;



1289  for (b_j = 0; b_j < 6400; b_j++) {



1290    y[b_j] = 0.0;



1291    NMPC_Controller_B.A[b_j] = x[b_j];



1292  }



1293



1294  for (b_j = 0; b_j < 80; b_j++) {



1295    ipiv[b_j] = 1 + b_j;



1296  }



1297



1298  for (b_j = 0; b_j < 79; b_j++) {



1299    c_c = b_j * 81;



1300    jA = 1;



1301    c = c_c;



1302    smax = fabs(NMPC_Controller_B.A[c_c]);



1303    for (j = 2; j <= 80 - b_j; j++) {



1304      c++;



1305      s = fabs(NMPC_Controller_B.A[c]);



1306      if (s > smax) {



1307        jA = j;



1308        smax = s;



1309      }



1310    }



1311



1312    if (NMPC_Controller_B.A[(c_c + jA) - 1] != 0.0) {



1313      if (jA - 1 != 0) {



1314        ipiv[b_j] = b_j + jA;



1315        NMPC_Controller_eml_xswap(NMPC_Controller_B.A, b_j + 1, b_j + jA);



1316      }



1317



1318      jA = (c_c - b_j) + 80;



1319      for (c = c_c + 1; c + 1 <= jA; c++) {



1320        NMPC_Controller_B.A[c] /= NMPC_Controller_B.A[c_c];



1321      }



1322    }



1323



1324    jA = c_c;



1325    c = c_c + 80;



1326    for (j = 1; j <= 79 - b_j; j++) {



1327      smax = NMPC_Controller_B.A[c];



1328      if (NMPC_Controller_B.A[c] != 0.0) {



1329        b_ix = c_c + 1;



1330        e = (jA - b_j) + 160;



1331        for (ijA = 81 + jA; ijA + 1 <= e; ijA++) {



1332          NMPC_Controller_B.A[ijA] += NMPC_Controller_B.A[b_ix] * -smax;



1333          b_ix++;



1334        }



1335      }



1336



1337      c += 80;



1338      jA += 80;



1339    }



1340  }



1341



1342  NMPC_Controller_eml_ipiv2perm(ipiv, p);



1343  for (jA = 0; jA < 80; jA++) {



1344    c = p[jA] - 1;



1345    y[jA + 80 * (p[jA] - 1)] = 1.0;



1346    for (j = jA; j + 1 < 81; j++) {



1347      if (y[80 * c + j] != 0.0) {



1348        for (b_ix = j + 1; b_ix + 1 < 81; b_ix++) {



1349          y[b_ix + 80 * c] -= y[80 * c + j] * NMPC_Controller_B.A[80 * j + b_ix];



1350        }



1351      }



1352    }



1353  }



1354



1355  NMPC_Controller_eml_xtrsm(NMPC_Controller_B.A, y);



1356}

1360{



1361  NMPC_Controller_invNxN(a, c);



1362}

1390/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/Control System' */



1391static void NMPC_Controller_eml_ipiv2perm_k(const int32_T ipiv_data[], const



1392  int32_T ipiv_sizes[2], int32_T m, int32_T perm_data[], int32_T perm_sizes[2])



1393{

1395  int32_T yk;



1396  perm_sizes[0] = 1;



1397  perm_sizes[1] = m;



1398  perm_data[0] = 1;



1399  yk = 1;



1400  for (pipk = 2; pipk <= m; pipk++) {



1401    yk++;



1402    perm_data[pipk - 1] = yk;



1403  }



1404



1405  for (yk = 0; yk < ipiv_sizes[1]; yk++) {

1407      pipk = perm_data[ipiv_data[yk] - 1];

1414/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/Control System' */



1415static void NMPC_Controller_eml_xtrsm_b(int32_T m, int32_T n, const real_T



1416  A_data[], int32_T lda, real_T B_data[], int32_T ldb)

1420  int32_T j;



1421  int32_T k;



1422  int32_T i;



1423  for (j = 1; j <= n; j++) {



1424    jBcol = (j - 1) * ldb;



1425    for (k = m - 1; k + 1 > 0; k--) {



1426      kAcol = lda * k;



1427      if (B_data[k + jBcol] != 0.0) {



1428        B_data[k + jBcol] /= A_data[k + kAcol];



1429        for (i = 0; i + 1 <= k; i++) {



1430          B_data[i + jBcol] -= B_data[k + jBcol] * A_data[i + kAcol];



1431        }



1432      }



1433    }



1434  }



1435}

1438static void NMPC_Controller_eml_xswap_d(int32_T n, real_T x_data[], int32_T ix0,

1456/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/Control System' */



1457static void NMPC_Controller_invNxN_l(const real_T x_data[], const int32_T



1458  x_sizes[2], real_T y_data[], int32_T y_sizes[2])



1459{



1460  int32_T n;



1461  int32_T i;



1462  int32_T mmj;



1463  int32_T b_j;



1464  int32_T c_c;



1465  int32_T yk;



1466  real_T smax;



1467  real_T s;



1468  int32_T jy;



1469  int32_T b_ix;



1470  int32_T f;



1471  int32_T ijA;



1472  int32_T loop_ub;



1473  int32_T p_data[120];



1474  int32_T p_sizes[2];



1475  int32_T A_sizes[2];



1476  int32_T ipiv_data[120];



1477  int32_T ipiv_sizes[2];



1478  int32_T u0;



1479  n = x_sizes[0];



1480  y_sizes[0] = x_sizes[0];



1481  y_sizes[1] = x_sizes[1];



1482  loop_ub = x_sizes[0] * x_sizes[1];



1483  for (yk = 0; yk < loop_ub; yk++) {



1484    y_data[yk] = 0.0;



1485  }



1486



1487  A_sizes[0] = x_sizes[0];



1488  A_sizes[1] = x_sizes[1];



1489  loop_ub = x_sizes[0] * x_sizes[1];



1490  for (yk = 0; yk < loop_ub; yk++) {



1491    NMPC_Controller_B.A_data[yk] = x_data[yk];



1492  }



1493



1494  loop_ub = x_sizes[0];



1495  ipiv_sizes[0] = 1;



1496  ipiv_sizes[1] = loop_ub;



1497  ipiv_data[0] = 1;



1498  yk = 1;



1499  for (jy = 2; jy <= loop_ub; jy++) {



1500    yk++;



1501    ipiv_data[jy - 1] = yk;



1502  }



1503



1504  u0 = x_sizes[0] - 1;



1505  if (!(u0 <= x_sizes[0])) {



1506    u0 = x_sizes[0];



1507  }



1508



1509  for (b_j = 1; b_j <= u0; b_j++) {



1510    mmj = (n - b_j) + 1;



1511    c_c = (b_j - 1) * (n + 1);



1512    if (mmj < 1) {



1513      loop_ub = -1;



1514    } else {



1515      loop_ub = 0;



1516      if (mmj > 1) {



1517        yk = c_c;



1518        smax = fabs(NMPC_Controller_B.A_data[c_c]);



1519        for (jy = 1; jy + 1 <= mmj; jy++) {



1520          yk++;



1521          s = fabs(NMPC_Controller_B.A_data[yk]);



1522          if (s > smax) {



1523            loop_ub = jy;



1524            smax = s;



1525          }



1526        }



1527      }



1528    }



1529



1530    if (NMPC_Controller_B.A_data[c_c + loop_ub] != 0.0) {



1531      if (loop_ub != 0) {



1532        ipiv_data[b_j - 1] = b_j + loop_ub;



1533        NMPC_Controller_eml_xswap_d(n, NMPC_Controller_B.A_data, b_j, n, b_j +



1534          loop_ub, n);



1535      }



1536



1537      loop_ub = c_c + mmj;



1538      for (yk = c_c + 1; yk + 1 <= loop_ub; yk++) {



1539        NMPC_Controller_B.A_data[yk] /= NMPC_Controller_B.A_data[c_c];



1540      }



1541    }



1542



1543    loop_ub = n - b_j;



1544    yk = c_c + n;



1545    jy = c_c + n;



1546    for (i = 1; i <= loop_ub; i++) {



1547      smax = NMPC_Controller_B.A_data[jy];



1548      if (NMPC_Controller_B.A_data[jy] != 0.0) {



1549        b_ix = c_c + 1;



1550        f = mmj + yk;



1551        for (ijA = 1 + yk; ijA + 1 <= f; ijA++) {



1552          NMPC_Controller_B.A_data[ijA] += NMPC_Controller_B.A_data[b_ix] *



1553            -smax;



1554          b_ix++;



1555        }



1556      }



1557



1558      jy += n;



1559      yk += n;



1560    }



1561  }



1562



1563  NMPC_Controller_eml_ipiv2perm_k(ipiv_data, ipiv_sizes, x_sizes[0], p_data,



1564    p_sizes);



1565  for (loop_ub = 0; loop_ub + 1 <= n; loop_ub++) {



1566    yk = p_data[loop_ub] - 1;



1567    y_data[loop_ub + y_sizes[0] * (p_data[loop_ub] - 1)] = 1.0;



1568    for (jy = loop_ub; jy + 1 <= n; jy++) {



1569      if (y_data[y_sizes[0] * yk + jy] != 0.0) {



1570        for (i = jy + 1; i + 1 <= n; i++) {



1571          y_data[i + y_sizes[0] * yk] -= y_data[y_sizes[0] * yk + jy] *



1572            NMPC_Controller_B.A_data[A_sizes[0] * jy + i];



1573        }



1574      }



1575    }



1576  }



1577



1578  NMPC_Controller_eml_xtrsm_b(x_sizes[0], x_sizes[0], NMPC_Controller_B.A_data,



1579    x_sizes[0], y_data, x_sizes[0]);



1580}

1594



1595real_T rt_roundd_snf(real_T u)



1596{



1597  real_T y;



1598  if (fabs(u) < 4.503599627370496E+15) {



1599    if (u >= 0.5) {



1600      y = floor(u + 0.5);



1601    } else if (u > -0.5) {



1602      y = u * 0.0;



1603    } else {



1604      y = ceil(u - 0.5);



1605    }



1606  } else {



1607    y = u;



1608  }



1609



1610  return y;



1611}

1879      Cns_k = *accelY_ann_k;



1880      mass = *accelZ_ann_k;



1881    }



1882  }



1883



1884  /* body accelerations */



1885  Udot_k = ((R_k * V_k - Q_k * W_k) - b_g * sin(theta_k)) + Cls_k;



1886  Vdot_k = ((P_k * W_k - R_k * U_k) + b_g * sin(phi_k) * cos(theta_k)) + Cns_k;



1887  Wdot_k = ((Q_k * U_k - P_k * V_k) + b_g * cos(phi_k) * cos(theta_k)) + mass;



1888



1889  /* %inertial speed (with no wind)%% */



1890  fn_k = ((sin(phi_k) * sin(theta_k) * cos(psi_k) - cos(phi_k) * sin(psi_k)) *



1891          V_k + U_k * cos(theta_k) * cos(psi_k)) + (cos(phi_k) * sin(theta_k) *



1892    cos(psi_k) + sin(phi_k) * sin(psi_k)) * W_k;



1893  fe_k = ((sin(phi_k) * sin(theta_k) * sin(psi_k) + cos(phi_k) * cos(psi_k)) *



1894          V_k + U_k * cos(theta_k) * sin(psi_k)) + (cos(phi_k) * sin(theta_k) *



1895    sin(psi_k) - sin(phi_k) * cos(psi_k)) * W_k;



1896  fh_k = (U_k * sin(theta_k) - V_k * sin(phi_k) * cos(theta_k)) - W_k * cos



1897    (phi_k) * cos(theta_k);



1898



1899  /* %inertial speed%% */



1900  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



1901  /* %%%uas at time [k]%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



1902  /* %%%trajectory logic at time [k]%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



1903  /* Local variable assignment */



1904  *wpt_index_kk = wpt_index_k;



1905  r_a = rt_roundd_snf(home_reset_k);



1906  if (r_a < 256.0) {



1907    if (r_a >= 0.0) {



1908      *home_reset_kk = (uint8_T)r_a;



1909    } else {



1910      *home_reset_kk = 0U;



1911    }



1912  } else {



1913    *home_reset_kk = MAX_uint8_T;



1914  }



1915



1916  /* PIC/CIC Transition Logic: */



1917  /*  On transition to CIC or PIC, set index = 0 and current position to  */



1918  /*  current waypoint; hold current waypoint. */



1919  if ((sw > pic_cic_k) || (sw == 0.0)) {



1920    start_wpt_k[0] = h_k;



1921    start_wpt_k[1] = n_k;



1922    start_wpt_k[2] = e_k;

1924    *home_reset_kk = 0U;



1925  }



1926



1927  /*  Change the waypoint index when home command */



1928  if ((home_cmd == 1) && (sw == 1.0) && (*home_reset_kk == 0)) {



1929    *wpt_index_kk = 23U;



1930    *home_reset_kk = 1U;



1931  }



1932



1933  /* OP trajectory generation */



1934  /* %reassigning the a and b waypoints */



1935  if ((b_TR == 2.0) && (*home_reset_kk == 0)) {



1936    *wpt_index_kk = 1U;

1938    factor = (int32_T)(wpt_index_k + 1U);



1939    if ((uint32_T)factor > 255U) {



1940      factor = 255;



1941    }



1942

1944    wpts_e[wpt_index_k - 1] = e_op_k - 100.0 * ve_op_k;



1945    factor = (int32_T)(wpt_index_k + 1U);



1946    if ((uint32_T)factor > 255U) {



1947      factor = 255;



1948    }



1949



1950    wpts_e[factor - 1] = 100.0 * ve_op_k + e_op_k;



1951    wpts_h[wpt_index_k - 1] = h_op_k - 100.0 * vh_op_k;



1952    factor = (int32_T)(wpt_index_k + 1U);



1953    if ((uint32_T)factor > 255U) {



1954      factor = 255;



1955    }



1956



1957    wpts_h[factor - 1] = 100.0 * vh_op_k + h_op_k;



1958  }



1959



1960  /* calculate the next waypoint index */



1961  factor = (int32_T)(*wpt_index_kk + 1U);



1962  if ((uint32_T)factor > 255U) {



1963    factor = 255;



1964  }



1965



1966  next_wpt_index = (uint8_T)factor;



1967



1968  /* beyond final point (fp), go to return point (rp) */



1969  if ((uint8_T)factor > wpts_fp) {



1970    next_wpt_index = wpts_rp;



1971  }



1972



1973  /* calculate distance to next waypoint */



1974  Cls_k = n_k - wpts_n[next_wpt_index - 1];



1975  Cns_k = e_k - wpts_e[next_wpt_index - 1];



1976  Cls_k = sqrt(Cls_k * Cls_k + Cns_k * Cns_k);



1977



1978  /* change to next waypoint if in range */



1979  if ((Cls_k < b_dist2b) && (sw == 1.0)) {



1980    /*  Do not change index if sw=0 */



1981    *wpt_index_kk = next_wpt_index;



1982    if (next_wpt_index == wpts_fp) {



1983      next_wpt_index = wpts_rp;



1984    } else {



1985      factor = (int32_T)(next_wpt_index + 1U);



1986      if ((uint32_T)factor > 255U) {



1987        factor = 255;



1988      }



1989



1990      next_wpt_index = (uint8_T)factor;



1991    }



1992  }



1993



1994  /* function outputs */



1995  if ((*wpt_index_kk == 0) || (*wpt_index_kk == 23)) {



1996    /*  Assign the speed of the starting segment to the speed of the first */



1997    /*  waypoint */



1998    *Vab_k = wpts_v[0];



1999    CL_k = start_wpt_k[0];



2000    CD_k = start_wpt_k[1];



2001    ea = start_wpt_k[2];



2002  } else {



2003    *Vab_k = wpts_v[*wpt_index_kk - 1];



2004    CL_k = wpts_h[*wpt_index_kk - 1];



2005    CD_k = wpts_n[*wpt_index_kk - 1];



2006    ea = wpts_e[*wpt_index_kk - 1];



2007  }



2008



2009  *distance2b = (real32_T)Cls_k;



2010  *pic_cic_kk = sw;



2011



2012  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



2013  /* %%%trajectory logic at time [k]%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



2014  /* %%%guidance system at time [k]%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



2015  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



2016  /* %reference point r%% */



2017  Cls_k = wpts_h[next_wpt_index - 1] - CL_k;



2018  Cns_k = wpts_n[next_wpt_index - 1] - CD_k;



2019  mass = wpts_e[next_wpt_index - 1] - ea;



2020  Cls_k = (((wpts_h[next_wpt_index - 1] - CL_k) * (h_k - CL_k) +



2021            (wpts_n[next_wpt_index - 1] - CD_k) * (n_k - CD_k)) +



2022           (wpts_e[next_wpt_index - 1] - ea) * (e_k - ea)) / ((Cls_k * Cls_k +



2023    Cns_k * Cns_k) + mass * mass);



2024  hd_k = (wpts_h[next_wpt_index - 1] - CL_k) * Cls_k + CL_k;



2025  nd_k = (wpts_n[next_wpt_index - 1] - CD_k) * Cls_k + CD_k;



2026  ed_k = (wpts_e[next_wpt_index - 1] - ea) * Cls_k + ea;



2027  Cls_k = wpts_h[next_wpt_index - 1] - hd_k;



2028  Cns_k = wpts_n[next_wpt_index - 1] - nd_k;



2029  mass = wpts_e[next_wpt_index - 1] - ed_k;



2030  Cls_k = b_L / sqrt((Cls_k * Cls_k + Cns_k * Cns_k) + mass * mass);



2031  *er_k = (wpts_e[next_wpt_index - 1] - ed_k) * Cls_k + ed_k;



2032  *nr_k = (wpts_n[next_wpt_index - 1] - nd_k) * Cls_k + nd_k;



2033  *hr_k = (wpts_h[next_wpt_index - 1] - hd_k) * Cls_k + hd_k;



2034



2035  /* %alpha and beta track%% */



2036  Cls_k = wpts_h[next_wpt_index - 1] - CL_k;



2037  Cns_k = wpts_n[next_wpt_index - 1] - CD_k;



2038  mass = wpts_e[next_wpt_index - 1] - ea;



2039  atrack = asin((wpts_h[next_wpt_index - 1] - CL_k) / sqrt((Cls_k * Cls_k +



2040    Cns_k * Cns_k) + mass * mass));



2041  Cls_k = wpts_n[next_wpt_index - 1] - CD_k;



2042  Cns_k = wpts_e[next_wpt_index - 1] - ea;



2043  factor = 1;



2044  mass = 0.0;



2045  if (!((wpts_n[next_wpt_index - 1] - CD_k > 0.0) && (wpts_e[next_wpt_index - 1]



2046        - ea > 0.0))) {

2048         - ea < 0.0)) {



2049      mass = 3.1415926535897931;



2050      factor = -1;



2051    } else {



2052      if ((wpts_n[next_wpt_index - 1] - CD_k < 0.0) && (wpts_e[next_wpt_index -



2053           1] - ea < 0.0)) {



2054        mass = -3.1415926535897931;



2055        factor = -1;



2056      }



2057    }



2058  }



2059



2060  btrack = asin((wpts_n[next_wpt_index - 1] - CD_k) / sqrt(Cls_k * Cls_k + Cns_k



2061    * Cns_k)) * (real_T)factor + mass;



2062



2063  /* %edot, ndot and hdot relative to track%% */



2064  edot_track_k = (sin(atrack) * cos(btrack) * fh_k + sin(btrack) * fn_k) + cos



2065    (atrack) * cos(btrack) * fe_k;



2066  ndot_track_k = (-sin(atrack) * sin(btrack) * fh_k + cos(btrack) * fn_k) - cos



2067    (atrack) * sin(btrack) * fe_k;



2068



2069  /* %er-e, nr-n and hr-h relative to track%% */



2070  /* %etaLon at time [k]%% */



2071  nr_k_0[0] = *nr_k - n_k;



2072  nr_k_0[1] = *er_k - e_k;



2073  fn_k_0[0] = fn_k;



2074  fn_k_0[1] = fe_k;



2075  *etaLon_k = rt_atan2d_snf(*hr_k - h_k, NMPC_Controller_norm(nr_k_0)) -



2076    rt_atan2d_snf(fh_k, NMPC_Controller_norm(fn_k_0));



2077



2078  /* %etaLat at time [k]%% */



2079  Cls_k = rt_atan2d_snf(ndot_track_k, edot_track_k) - rt_atan2d_snf((-sin(atrack)



2080    * sin(btrack) * (*hr_k - h_k) + (*nr_k - n_k) * cos(btrack)) - cos(atrack) *



2081    sin(btrack) * (*er_k - e_k), (sin(atrack) * cos(btrack) * (*hr_k - h_k) +



2082    (*nr_k - n_k) * sin(btrack)) + cos(atrack) * cos(btrack) * (*er_k - e_k));



2083  *etaLat_k = Cls_k;



2084  if (Cls_k > 3.1415926535897931) {



2085    *etaLat_k = Cls_k - 6.2831853071795862;



2086  }



2087



2088  if (Cls_k < -3.1415926535897931) {



2089    *etaLat_k = Cls_k + 6.2831853071795862;



2090  }



2091



2092  /* OP trajectory generation */



2093  /* reassigning Vab (based on the new d point) */



2094  if (b_TR == 2.0) {



2095    CL_k = wpts_n[next_wpt_index - 1] - n_op_k;



2096    CD_k = wpts_e[next_wpt_index - 1] - e_op_k;



2097    ea = wpts_h[next_wpt_index - 1] - h_op_k;



2098    r_a = wpts_n[next_wpt_index - 1] - nd_k;



2099    s_a = wpts_e[next_wpt_index - 1] - ed_k;



2100    t_a = wpts_h[next_wpt_index - 1] - hd_k;



2101    mass = nd_k - n_op_k;



2102    Cns_k = ed_k - e_op_k;



2103    Cls_k = hd_k - h_op_k;



2104    r_a = sqrt((CL_k * CL_k + CD_k * CD_k) + ea * ea) - sqrt((r_a * r_a + s_a *



2105      s_a) + t_a * t_a);



2106    if (r_a < 0.0) {



2107      r_a = -1.0;



2108    } else if (r_a > 0.0) {



2109      r_a = 1.0;



2110    } else {



2111      if (r_a == 0.0) {



2112        r_a = 0.0;



2113      }



2114    }



2115



2116    *Vab_k = sqrt((vn_op_k * vn_op_k + ve_op_k * ve_op_k) + vh_op_k * vh_op_k) -



2117      atan(sqrt((mass * mass + Cns_k * Cns_k) + Cls_k * Cls_k) * r_a / 100.0) *



2118      0.063661977236758135;



2119



2120    /* (168.78) (5) (/100) */



2121  }



2122



2123  /* %VT theta phi and beta command%% */



2124  /* %consider wind in VTcmd [0]: no [1]:yes */



2125  mass = *Vab_k * cos(atrack) * sin(btrack) + 0.0 * sw;



2126  Cns_k = *Vab_k * cos(atrack) * cos(btrack) + 0.0 * sw;



2127  Cls_k = *Vab_k * sin(atrack) + 0.0 * sw;



2128  *VTcmd_k = sqrt((mass * mass + Cns_k * Cns_k) + Cls_k * Cls_k);



2129  Cls_k = atan(*etaLon_k * sw);



2130  er_k_1[0] = *er_k - e_k;



2131  er_k_1[1] = *nr_k - n_k;



2132  er_k_1[2] = *hr_k - h_k;



2133  *thetacmd_k = rt_atan2d_snf(((fe_k * fe_k + fn_k * fn_k) + fh_k * fh_k) * 2.0 *



2134                              (Cls_k * b_KpLon + ro_k), NMPC_Controller_norm_l



2135    (er_k_1));



2136  er_k_0[0] = *er_k - e_k;



2137  er_k_0[1] = *nr_k - n_k;



2138  *phicmd_k = rt_atan2d_snf((edot_track_k * edot_track_k + ndot_track_k *



2139    ndot_track_k) * 2.0 * b_KpLat * sw * *etaLat_k, NMPC_Controller_norm(er_k_0));



2140



2141  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



2142  /* %%%guidance system at time [k]%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



2143  /* %%%implementing saturation of actuators%% */



2144  /* %deflection max and min */



2145  if (THL_k > b_ThrottleMax) {



2146    THL_k = b_ThrottleMax;



2147  } else {



2148    if (THL_k < b_ThrottleMin) {



2149      THL_k = b_ThrottleMin;



2150    }



2151  }



2152



2153  if (EL_k > b_ElevatorMax) {



2154    EL_k = b_ElevatorMax;



2155  } else {



2156    if (EL_k < b_ElevatorMin) {



2157      EL_k = b_ElevatorMin;



2158    }



2159  }



2160



2161  if (AIL_k > b_AileronMax) {



2162    AIL_k = b_AileronMax;



2163  } else {



2164    if (AIL_k < b_AileronMin) {



2165      AIL_k = b_AileronMin;



2166    }



2167  }



2168



2169  if (RDR_k > b_RudderMax) {



2170    RDR_k = b_RudderMax;



2171  } else {



2172    if (RDR_k < b_RudderMin) {



2173      RDR_k = b_RudderMin;



2174    }



2175  }



2176



2177  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



2178  /* %%%prediction of kk%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



2179  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



2180  /* %longitudinal guidance integrator */



2181  *ro_kk = b_dt * Cls_k * b_KiLon + ro_k;



2182



2183  /* %servos prediction%% */



2184  *THL_kk = (b_Athrottle * THL_k + b_Bthrottle * THLcmd_k) * b_dt + THL_k;



2185  *EL_kk = (b_Aelevator * EL_k + b_Belevator * ELcmd_k) * b_dt + EL_k;



2186  *AIL_kk = (b_Aaileron * AIL_k + b_Baileron * AILcmd_k) * b_dt + AIL_k;



2187  *RDR_kk = (b_Arudder * RDR_k + b_Brudder * RDRcmd_k) * b_dt + RDR_k;



2188



2189  /* %UAV prediction%% */



2190  Cls_k = ((U_k * Udot_k + V_k * Vdot_k) + W_k * Wdot_k) / VT_k;



2191  *falpha_k = (U_k * Wdot_k - W_k * Udot_k) / (U_k * U_k + W_k * W_k);



2192  *fbeta_k = (VT_k * Vdot_k - V_k * Cls_k) / (U_k * U_k + W_k * W_k) * cos



2193    (beta_k);

2196  *beta_kk = b_dt * *fbeta_k + beta_k;

2198    + phi_k;

2200  *psi_kk = (R_k * cos(phi_k) + Q_k * sin(phi_k)) / cos(theta_k) * b_dt + psi_k;



2201  *P_kk = ((((b_IyyB - b_IzzB) * b_IzzB - b_IxzB * b_IxzB) / delta_I * R_k + c2 *



2202            P_k) * Q_k + (b_IzzB / delta_I * Cl_k + c4 * Cn_k) * (Qbar_k * b_S *



2203            b_b)) * b_dt + P_k;

2208            R_k) * Q_k + (b_IxxB / delta_I * Cn_k + c4 * Cl_k) * (Qbar_k * b_S *



2209            b_b)) * b_dt + R_k;



2210

2213  *e_kk = b_dt * fe_k + e_k;

3210      for (i = 0; i <= ii_sizes_idx_1; i++) {

3291  for (idx = 0; idx < 20; idx++) {

3317  }

3326}

3726  /* %reference point r%% */



3727  Cls_k = wpts_h[next_wpt_index - 1] - CL_k;

3750    Cns_k * Cns_k) + mass * mass));

3790    * sin(btrack) * (*hr_k - h_k) + (*nr_k - n_k) * cos(btrack)) - cos(atrack) *



3791    sin(btrack) * (*er_k - e_k), (sin(atrack) * cos(btrack) * (*hr_k - h_k) +

3800  }



3801



3802  /* OP trajectory generation */



3803  /* reassigning Vab (based on the new d point) */



3804  if (b_TR == 2.0) {

3815      s_a) + t_a * t_a);

3886



3887  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



3888  /* %%%prediction of kk%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



3889  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



3890  /* %longitudinal guidance integrator */



3891  *ro_kk = b_dt * Cls_k * b_KiLon + ro_k;



3892



3893  /* %servos prediction%% */



3894  *THL_kk = (b_Athrottle * THL_k + b_Bthrottle * THLcmd_k) * b_dt + THL_k;



3895  *EL_kk = (b_Aelevator * EL_k + b_Belevator * ELcmd_k) * b_dt + EL_k;



3896  *AIL_kk = (b_Aaileron * AIL_k + b_Baileron * AILcmd_k) * b_dt + AIL_k;



3897  *RDR_kk = (b_Arudder * RDR_k + b_Brudder * RDRcmd_k) * b_dt + RDR_k;



3898



3899  /* %UAV prediction%% */



3900  Cls_k = ((U_k * Udot_k + V_k * Vdot_k) + W_k * Wdot_k) / VT_k;



3901  *falpha_k = (U_k * Wdot_k - W_k * Udot_k) / (U_k * U_k + W_k * W_k);



3902  *fbeta_k = (VT_k * Vdot_k - V_k * Cls_k) / (U_k * U_k + W_k * W_k) * cos



3903    (beta_k);



3904  *VT_kk = b_dt * Cls_k + VT_k;



3905  *alpha_kk = b_dt * *falpha_k + alpha_k;



3906  *beta_kk = b_dt * *fbeta_k + beta_k;



3907  *phi_kk = ((R_k * cos(phi_k) + Q_k * sin(phi_k)) * tan(theta_k) + P_k) * b_dt



3908    + phi_k;



3909  *theta_kk = (Q_k * cos(phi_k) - R_k * sin(phi_k)) * b_dt + theta_k;



3910  *psi_kk = (R_k * cos(phi_k) + Q_k * sin(phi_k)) / cos(theta_k) * b_dt + psi_k;



3911  *P_kk = ((((b_IyyB - b_IzzB) * b_IzzB - b_IxzB * b_IxzB) / delta_I * R_k + c2 *



3912            P_k) * Q_k + (b_IzzB / delta_I * Cl_k + c4 * Cn_k) * (Qbar_k * b_S *



3913            b_b)) * b_dt + P_k;



3914  *Q_kk = (((b_IzzB - b_IxxB) / b_IyyB * P_k * R_k - (P_k * P_k - R_k * R_k) *



3915            (b_IxzB / b_IyyB)) + Qbar_k * b_S * b_Cbar * (1.0 / b_IyyB) * Cms_k)



3916    * b_dt + Q_k;



3917  *R_kk = ((((b_IxxB - b_IyyB) * b_IxxB + b_IxzB * b_IxzB) / delta_I * P_k - c2 *



3918            R_k) * Q_k + (b_IxxB / delta_I * Cn_k + c4 * Cl_k) * (Qbar_k * b_S *



3919            b_b)) * b_dt + R_k;



3920



3921  /* %inertial frame prediction%% */



3922  *n_kk = b_dt * fn_k + n_k;



3923  *e_kk = b_dt * fe_k + e_k;



3924  *h_kk = b_dt * fh_k + h_k;



3925



3926  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



3927  /* %%%prediction of kk%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



3928  /* %%%Robustness nmpc calculations%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



3929  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



3930  /* %outputs e, y and z%% */



3931  e_augm_k[0] = *VTcmd_k - VT_k;



3932  e_augm_k[1] = *thetacmd_k - theta_k;



3933  e_augm_k[2] = *phicmd_k - phi_k;



3934  e_augm_k[3] = 0.0 - beta_k;



3935



3936  /* %Robustness states at [k+1]%% */



3937  *xw11_kk = b_W11d.a * xw11_k + b_W11d.b * e_augm_k[0];



3938



3939  /* W11 e_VT */



3940  *xw12_kk = b_W12d.a * xw12_k + b_W12d.b * e_augm_k[1];



3941



3942  /* W12 e_theta */



3943  *xw13_kk = b_W13d.a * xw13_k + b_W13d.b * e_augm_k[2];



3944



3945  /* W13 e_phi */



3946  *xw14_kk = (0.0 - beta_k) * b_W14d.b + b_W14d.a * xw14_k;



3947



3948  /* W14 e_beta */



3949  *xw21_kk = b_W21d.a * xw21_k + b_W21d.b * THLcmd_k;



3950



3951  /* W21 Throttle cmd */



3952  *xw22_kk = b_W22d.a * xw22_k + b_W22d.b * ELcmd_k;



3953



3954  /* W22 Elevator cmd */



3955  *xw23_kk = b_W23d.a * xw23_k + b_W23d.b * AILcmd_k;



3956



3957  /* W23 Aileron cmd */



3958  *xw24_kk = b_W24d.a * xw24_k + b_W24d.b * RDRcmd_k;



3959



3960  /* W24 Rudder cmd */



3961  *xw31_kk = b_W31d.a * xw31_k + b_W31d.b * VT_k;



3962



3963  /* W31 VT */



3964  *xw32_kk = b_W32d.a * xw32_k + b_W32d.b * theta_k;



3965



3966  /* W32 theta */



3967  *xw33_kk = b_W33d.a * xw33_k + b_W33d.b * phi_k;



3968



3969  /* W33 phi */



3970  *xw34_kk = b_W34d.a * xw34_k + b_W34d.b * beta_k;



3971



3972  /* W34 beta */



3973  /* %Robustness output at [k] */



3974  z_augm_k[0] = b_W11d.c * xw11_k + b_W11d.d * e_augm_k[0];



3975



3976  /* W11 e_VT */



3977  z_augm_k[1] = b_W12d.c * xw12_k + b_W12d.d * e_augm_k[1];



3978



3979  /* W12 e_theta */



3980  z_augm_k[2] = b_W13d.c * xw13_k + b_W13d.d * e_augm_k[2];



3981



3982  /* W13 e_phi */



3983  z_augm_k[3] = (0.0 - beta_k) * b_W14d.d + b_W14d.c * xw14_k;



3984



3985  /* W14 e_beta */



3986  z_augm_k[4] = b_W21d.c * xw21_k + b_W21d.d * THLcmd_k;



3987



3988  /* W21 Throttle cmd */



3989  z_augm_k[5] = b_W22d.c * xw22_k + b_W22d.d * ELcmd_k;



3990



3991  /* W22 Elevator cmd */



3992  z_augm_k[6] = b_W23d.c * xw23_k + b_W23d.d * AILcmd_k;



3993



3994  /* W23 Aileron cmd */



3995  z_augm_k[7] = b_W24d.c * xw24_k + b_W24d.d * RDRcmd_k;



3996



3997  /* W24 Rudder cmd */



3998  z_augm_k[8] = b_W31d.c * xw31_k + b_W31d.d * VT_k;



3999



4000  /* W31 VT */



4001  z_augm_k[9] = b_W32d.c * xw32_k + b_W32d.d * theta_k;



4002



4003  /* W32 theta */



4004  z_augm_k[10] = b_W33d.c * xw33_k + b_W33d.d * phi_k;



4005



4006  /* W33 phi */



4007  z_augm_k[11] = b_W34d.c * xw34_k + b_W34d.d * beta_k;



4008



4009  /* W34 beta */



4010  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



4011  /* %%%Robustness nmpc calculations%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



4012}
